Using ACI API -

REST API call makes backend database query on the APIC server

Cobra SDK - 2 components must be installed -

- ACI Cobra - interacts directly with the server
- ACI Model - structures the data

Also ACI Toolkit - available on github

Strucutre of API call:

1. Request is made over HTTP - api/class or managed object/ name or DN.json? (almost identical to nxapi rest)
2. Everything in the GUI/Dashboard is reachable via API - use browser inspect or use API inpector in settings
